    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty ride! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. It drives beautifully and is ready to hit the road for its next big adventure. If you're looking for a dependable car that\u2019s been well-cared for, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have!",
      "price": 31500.0,
